title: Curry.Wars.S01E01-E02.480p.HDTV.x264-RMTeam
description:
Curry Wars is a two-part series following the hottest competition in Wales - the race for the crown every curry house in the nation wants to win. It's a case of north versus south, versus mid and west as restaurants go head to head to prove that their version of the nation's favourite dish cannot be beaten. Hundreds will enter, but only one can claim the ultimate crown of Welsh Curry House of the Year.




Original Air Dates: 17-18.Sep.2015
